title: #92Noon Live from TCO: Zimmer / Spielman / Birk / Warren
description:
The FAN's Paul Allen and Eric Nordquist broadcast live from OTAs at the TCO Performance Center.

Guests include Mike Zimmer, Rick Spielman, Mike Wobschall, Matt Birk, and Kevin Warren!
